nodes.text: Cheese was a type of food. Shortly after the destruction of the planet Alderaan, an old man operating the stall known as Hangra's Meat Shack on the planet Coruscant gave some scraps of meat and cheese to the human fugitive Anandra Milon when she approached him and seemed confused. Ananadra later ate the meat and cheese with her brother Santigo Milon in an alley. Falumpaset cheese was a type of cheese that served as an ingredient in the dish mashed chokeroot, which was served in the restaurant Tuggs' Grub on the Outer Rim planet Batuu.
